lead_paragraph: Swansea City must learn to kill off teams by scoring at least two goals, goalkeeper Lukasz Fabianski said as the club seek to keep out of the Premier League's relegation dogfight.

headline.print_headline: Swansea Must Kill Off Games Not Hold On to Them-Fabianski
headline.main: Swansea Must Kill Off Games Not Hold On to Them-Fabianski
